description: Where their lives intersected and what may have influenced them.
title: The Links Among the Paris Terror Suspects and Their Connections to Jihad
title_page: The Links Among the Paris Terror Suspects and Their Connections to Jihad - The New York Times
maintext:
Al Qaeda Trained Suspect in Paris Terror Attack, Official Says
Saïd Kouachi, 34, one of the two brothers suspected of killing 12 people at a newspaper, spent “a few months” with an Al Qaeda affiliate in Yemen, a U.S. official said.
